OL,10,GThe Windows 365 Link is a thin client,
OL,11,Grunning a special edition of Windows
OL,12,G11, that can only connect to a
OL,13,G"Windows 365 Cloud PC" and is
OL,14,Gotherwise useless ewaste. When it was
OL,15,Gannounced, Microsoft boasted its total
OL,16,Gvendor lock-in plan, which they
OL,17,Gdescribed as "secure-by-design
OL,18,Garchitecture": no admin rights, no
OL,19,Glocal data, EFI Secure Boot locked on,
OL,20,GBitLocker always enabled. The last
OL,22,D]CEMFFAX: The world at your fingertips\
